# Installation Guide

{{#if analyzer.[package.json] }}
## NPM

This project uses [NPM](https://npmjs.org/) to manage it's Node dependencies.

Learn more about NPM [here](https://docs.npmjs.com/getting-started/what-is-npm).

Fetch any requirements using the following command:

    $ npm install
{{/if}}

{{#if analyzer.[composer.json] }}
## Composer

This project uses [composer](https://getcomposer.org/doc/00-intro.md) to manage it's PHP dependencies.

Learn more about Composer [here](https://getcomposer.org/doc/00-intro.md)

Fetch any requirements using the following command:

    $ composer install
{{/if}}
